2 JOHN 

YHWH (YHYYH) Codex

FULL REVERSE COHERENT SCAN
Codex YHWH (YHYYH) w/ Numerical Letter Differentiation
Numerical Note: YHWH (יהוה) = 26 base. YHYYH variant = 36 intensified (doubled Yod for covenant/redemptive emphasis). Literal root fidelity to Masoretic/Septuagint tradition with YHWH framework.


Peace be with you. The children of your elect sister greet you.
Though I have much to write to you I would rather not use paper and ink but I hope to come to you and talk face to face so that our joy may be complete.
For many deceivers have gone out into world those who do not confess coming of Yeshua the Anointed in flesh. Such one is deceiver and antichrist. Watch yourselves so that you may not lose what we have worked for but may win full reward. Anyone who goes on ahead and does not abide in teaching of Anointed does not have YHWH. Whoever abides in teaching has both Father and Son. If anyone comes to you and does not bring this teaching do not receive him into house or give him any greeting for whoever greets him takes part in his wicked works.
And now I ask you lady — not as though I were writing you new commandment but one we have had from beginning — that we love one another. And this is love that we walk according to His commandments. This is commandment just as you have heard from beginning so that you should walk in it.
I rejoiced greatly to find some of your children walking in truth just as we were commanded by Father.
The elder to elect lady and her children whom I love in truth and not only I but also all who know truth because of truth that abides in us and will be with us forever. Grace mercy and peace will be with us from YHWH Father and from Yeshua the Anointed Son of Father in truth and love.
